      <title>Asynchronous APIs</title>
      <link>https://buenhyden.github.io/posts/software-engineering/design-and-architecture/architecture-styles-and-patterns/architecture-styles/distributed/client-server-architecture/request-response-cycle/asynchronous/</link>
